      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WHISKY BENT (2) has a strong overall record having four wins and nine places from 16 starts including a last start third (23.44) over 400m at this track. Form here sound including three wins. Has the ability and looks a key chance this line-up. IMPERATOR (1) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (23.49) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Safe beginner and drawn well on the inside. Can turn it around this time. DRINK TO THAT (5) box seated before sticking on well to finish 7 lengths away in third (23.11) at this track in a Grade 5 over 400m. Expected to feature again. BLUE LEGEND (6) placed two back in a Grade 5 at Taree Super Track then backed that up with a second (23.62) over 400m at this track last time. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a tricky draw.",
